subject: packaging: fix the ARM build
commitMessage:
packaging: fix the ARM build

If we are building for ARM, and are linking with the
"libwinpr-makecert.a" temporary library, it may fail if the
object files were not all created with the "-fPIC" flag.

Change-Id: Id70609ba11abcab8b5a45be1a37e8194a4c1a79c
Signed-off-by: Manuel Bachmann <manuel.bachmann@open.eurogiciel.org>
